#IOTA released Spark, a web wallet that can be both set up and erased in seconds. Spark’s main feature is privacy. Whenever a Spark wallet is burned, its transaction history is gone forever. Burning doesn’t remove data from IOTA’s ledger, but it does remove it from the wallet.
